{
  "name": "01 — Entrada: Webhook Receiver (Hotmart)",
  "active": false,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "w1-note-001",
      "name": "Nota — Configuração",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 60],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Fluxo 01 — Webhook Receiver (Hotmart)\n\n**Credencial necessária:** Supabase — jornada_alunos\n**Configurar em:** Settings → Credentials → Add → Supabase\n\n**Filtro de evento:** processa apenas `PURCHASE_COMPLETE` (outros eventos são ignorados silenciosamente).\n\n**Lógica aluno (upsert manual por email):**\n1. Tenta criar → se 409 (já existe), busca pelo email\n2. Merge garante que o id do aluno segue para as próximas etapas\n\n**Lógica produto (upsert manual por nome):**\n1. Tenta criar → se 409 (já existe), busca pelo nome\n2. Merge garante que o id do produto segue para criar aluno_produtos\n\n**URL do webhook:**\nhttps://[seu-n8n]/webhook/hotmart",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 900
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w1-node-001",
      "name": "Hotmart — Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [240, 400],
      "webhookId": "hotmart-entrada-001",
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "hotmart",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w1-node-ev",
      "name": "Evento Válido?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [460, 400],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": { "caseSensitive": true, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "loose" },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-evento-valido",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.body.event }}",
              "rightValue": "PURCHASE_COMPLETE",
              "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w1-node-002",
      "name": "Normalizar Campos",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [680, 400],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "manual",
        "fields": {
          "values": [
            {
              "name": "nome",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.buyer.name }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "whatsapp",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.buyer.checkout_phone?.toString().replace(/\\D/g, '') }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "email",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.buyer.email }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "cidade",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.buyer.address?.city ?? null }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "estado",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.buyer.address?.state ?? null }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "order_id",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.purchase.transaction }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "valor",
              "type": "numberValue",
              "numberValue": "={{ $json.body.data.purchase.price.value }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "metodo_pagamento",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.purchase.payment.type }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "status",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.purchase.status }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "event",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.event }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "produto",
              "type": "stringValue",
              "stringValue": "={{ $json.body.data.product.name }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "dados_raw",
              "type": "objectValue",
              "objectValue": "={{ $json.body }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w1-node-003",
      "name": "Supabase — Create Aluno",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [900, 400],
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput",
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "create",
        "tableId": "alunos",
        "fieldsUi": {
          "fieldValues": [
            { "fieldId": "nome",     "fieldValue": "={{ $json.nome }}" },
            { "fieldId": "email",    "fieldValue": "={{ $json.email }}" },
            { "fieldId": "whatsapp", "fieldValue": "={{ $json.whatsapp }}" },
            { "fieldId": "cidade",   "fieldValue": "={{ $json.cidade }}" },
            { "fieldId": "estado",   "fieldValue": "={{ $json.estado }}" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "credentials": {
        "supabaseApi": {
          "id": "SUPABASE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Supabase — jornada_alunos"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w1-node-005",
      "name": "Aluno Criado?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1120, 400],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": { "caseSensitive": false, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "loose" },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-aluno-id",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.id }}",
              "rightValue": "",
              "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "notEmpty", "singleValue": true }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w1-node-006",
      "name": "Supabase — Buscar Aluno",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1340, 540],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "getAll",
        "tableId": "alunos",
        "returnAll": false,
        "limit": 1,
        "filters": {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "keyName": "email",
              "condition": "eq",
              "keyValue": "={{ $('Normalizar Campos').item.json.email }}"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "credentials": {
        "supabaseApi": {
          "id": "SUPABASE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Supabase — jornada_alunos"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w1-node-007",
      "name": "Merge — Aluno",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.merge",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [1560, 400],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "append",
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
